"искусственных сооружений собственной техникой и силами бригад."
msgstr ""
"We perform earthworks, track superstructure laying and construction of "
"engineering structures with our own equipment and crews."

#: templates/core/homepage.html:87
msgid "Пусконаладка"
msgstr "Commissioning"

#: templates/core/homepage.html:88
