"остановкой производства заказчика."
msgstr ""
"We modernise existing private railway tracks — from ballast reinforcement to "
"complete relaying of the rail-and-sleeper grid. We work with minimal "
"disruption to the client’s operations."

#: templates/core/homepage.html:256
